Recap of from last weekend’s nationals 2022! @npcnationals 
Happy to end this year on a positive note. The beginning of this year started out rough. One bad thing after another! No offseason.  To starting one of my best preps ever!  At times it didn’t even feel like I was in prep 🍔🍔🍔. I literally grew through out this prep and gained back the muscle I lost from not training. I definitely enjoyed every minute of this prep. Now to finally have a legit offseason so that I can grow.
